ly to the audience during the workshop.\n<\/dd>\n<dt>Important Dates<\/dt>\n<dd>\n<table class=\"plain\">\n<tr>\n<td><s>Submission due<\/td>\n<td><s>Mar. 17, 23:59<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><s>Author notification<\/td>\n<td><s>Mar. 24<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><s>Submission due<\/td>\n<td><s>Apr. 14, 23:59<\/td>\n<td><s>(extended)&lt;\/td<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td><s>Author notification<\/td>\n<td><s>Mar. 24<\/td>\n<td><s>(extended)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Electronic version due<\/td>\n<td>Apr. 17, 23:59<\/td>\n<td>(extended)<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Poster session<\/td>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><a href=\"\/en\/program\/\">Apr. 25th, 16:15\u201318:15<\/a><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/table>\n<\/dd>\n<\/dl>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Call for Posters We invite the submission of proposals for poster presentations at xSIG 2017. Our scope includ [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/563"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=563"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/563\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=563"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}